snippet.title: Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
snippet.description:
Authored and Created by Asit Kumarr Modi and produced by Neela Film Productions Private Limited, Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah (TMKOC) is an ongoing Indian television show that was first aired on July 28, 2008 and has till date completed over 3200 episodes

SUBSCRIBE to keep yourself updated with the latest on TMKOC, interact with the cast, and have a hearty laugh..!
